{"title":"谁活在我们心当中","authors":["曹禺"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":6,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁活在我们心当中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“六一”儿童节，小学生方子、元元、乃华朗诵的一首诗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曹禺三个孩子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣鼓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响堂堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声笑声遍四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天“六一”儿童节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满屋照着好阳光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁开眼睛喜鹊叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈叫我快起床。方子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，那是什么？三个孩子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红领巾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮光光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端端正正放桌上。乃华："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起红领巾，方子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我忍不住笑，元元："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我忍不住讲，三个孩子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向妈妈说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我要做新中国的好儿童，永远跟着共产党。”方子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我九岁，乃华："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我九岁半，元元："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我十岁，三个孩子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我戴上红领巾，方子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一，上课时间不说话，一心专听老师讲。乃华："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我对同学有礼貌，处处做个好榜样。元元："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第三，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动好，体格壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功课还要样样强。三个孩子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光得“优”不成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要做“三好”学生呢！三个孩子："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石榴花儿开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油菜花儿黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天还是小麦种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天翻起一片绿麦浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁下的雨？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁吹的风？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁活在我们心当中？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁告诉我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是坏；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁告诉我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是“白”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么是“红”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁告诉我们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动才是最光荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁把我们抚育大？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是亲爱的共产党！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是亲爱的毛主席！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}